sections.heading: Teams; exempt from Open Meetings Act
sections.text: The teams established by sections 28-728 to 28-730 shall not be considered a public body for purposes of the Open Meetings Act.SourceLaws 1992, LB 1184, ยง 4;Laws 2004, LB 821, ยง 10.Cross ReferencesOpen Meetings Act, see section 84-1407.
